Judges 5-31 <pb/><t><f>ⓜ</f> “So may all your enemies perish, O LORD! </t><t>But your friends be <f>ⓝ</f>like the sun <f>ⓞ</f>as he rises in his might.” </t> <pb/><f>ⓟ</f>And the land had rest for forty years.